observe.desc:
[
{A shelter that fully shields from the outside world, including light.}
]

[
{The P company wished to build the safest place on Earth. As such, the interior housed a large amount of long lasting supplies, which would allow anyone who stayed inside to survive for a very long period of time.}
]

[
{Thanks to the shelter, the selected refugees were shielded from the ocean of screaming and bloodshed.}
]

[
{But the shelter, while perfectly safe inside, alters the perception of the outside to be even more hopeless. It literally becomes, "The safest place on Earth."}
]
